<div>The following are some frequently asked questions about installing and</div><div>using ITOM Container Deployment Foundation (CDF).</div><div><br></div><div><br></div><div>What are the recommended deployment modes for CDF?</div><div><br></div><div>-&nbsp; &nbsp;One master node, at least three worker nodes, and a separate NFS</div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; server.</div><div>-&nbsp; &nbsp;Multiple master nodes, at least three worker nodes, and a separate</div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; NFS server.</div><div><br></div><div><br></div><div>Can I upgrade the suite images in CDF?</div><div><br></div><div>You will need to log in the management portal, click SUITE</div><div>&gt; [[22185968.PNG][]] &gt; UPDATE to upgrade suite.</div><div><br></div><div>&nbsp; [22185968.PNG]: https://docs.microfocus.com/mediawiki/images/f/fb/2018.04/attachments/17859066/22185968.png</div>